{"TopicId":215356,"ForumId":120,"TopicTitle":"Please Delay Flight Report Pop-up after Crash - (what happened to Unique Explosions?)","CreatedByName":"JoeSchmuckatelli","CreatedById":154477,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-17T18:59:01Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"JoeSchmuckatelli","CreatedById":154477,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-17T18:59:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI want to watch the crash!\u00A0 The instant pop up defeats this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso - there are times when my ship just seems to vanish - this is especially true for spaceplanes during reentry.\u00A0 Just *POOF* with the unnecessary \u0026amp; immediate Flight Report blocking 1/2 the screen.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d really like to see what happened to the ship... not a poof - and when it does go BOOM - not Pretentious Kerman\u0027s Unnecessary Flight Report.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Picard2","CreatedById":227404,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-17T20:16:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224261201\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022215356\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221679079541\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154477\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JoeSchmuckatelli\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, JoeSchmuckatelli said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI want to watch the crash!\u00A0 The instant pop up defeats this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes! I hadn\u0027t realised why the post-incident report felt so jarring, but this is exactly it - the instant you crash it\u0027s there up in your face.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Donkey32","CreatedById":174169,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-18T17:22:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAgreed!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tazooka","CreatedById":226666,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-18T20:58:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u002B1 good suggestion\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nuggzy","CreatedById":194703,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-19T13:48:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou aren\u0027t supposed to crash,\u00A0but if there is going to flaming Kerbal meteors, we definitely want to see them!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u002B1\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DaveLChgo","CreatedById":179012,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-20T01:42:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u002B1\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JoeSchmuckatelli","CreatedById":154477,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-20T01:43:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFinally had a crash without the report.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGlorious:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/Njl0TRXNyTQ?feature=oembed\u0022 title=\u0022The Most Kerbal crash since starting with KSP2 EA\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-20T07:44:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRather than delay it, I would prefer having to hit esc or some other key to bring it up rather than it being automatic.\u00A0 In KSP1 I could sometimes limp my broken craft into the air or off the runway. In the current set up, I am locked from doing anything.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd yes, I want to see things like this again!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022uYKI6zI.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/uYKI6zI.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022P4JRvxl.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/P4JRvxl.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-03-20T07:47:44Z\u0022 title=\u002203/20/2023 07:47  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 20, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Klapaucius\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Picard2","CreatedById":227404,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-21T09:45:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224262623\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022215356\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221679298241\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022181256\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Klapaucius\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 3/20/2023 at 7:44 AM, Klapaucius said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRather than delay it, I would prefer having to hit esc or some other key to bring it up rather than it being automatic.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe a floating \u0027Report\u0027 button appears at the top / bottom of the screen you can click to open the report?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}